[00:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'What\'s up everybody? Lurk Tech here and welcome back to build with me episode 3. If you\'d followed along since episode 1, you already know the drill. We\'re not copying templates here. We\'re building node by node, so you actually understand what\'s happening under the hood. And today we\'re doing something a lot of you'

[00:13] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'have been asking about, in-painting. Specifically, editing one part of a photo, like swapping out an outfit for example, without touching at the rest of the image. And without manually painting a mask yourself, because that gets tedious and annoying sometimes. We\'re'

[00:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'going to let a model called SAM 3 read a text prompt and generate that mask automatically. It does a very, very good job at painting a detailed mask with just a very, very simple prompt, such as'

[00:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'person or face or shirt. If you\'re brand new to ComfyUI, go watch episode 1 and 2 first. It covers the absolute basics. If you already got a basic build down, you\'re in the right place.'

